## Overall task (the goal this scouting supports)
Move the 'actions' buttons on each row into a drop-down menu that appears below the new menu button (three vertical dots should be visible on the currently hovered row, else be hidden. No border/background, muted foreground, hover on the button: foreground color change from muted to normal). The columns should adjust for this: File name becomes 'flex: 1'-like (stretch). File size and modified datetime and the actions columns should be aligned-right. The actions column doesn't need a header now (3 vertical dots on the rows is enough). Whenever the user right-clicks on the file/folder row, the SAME menu should appear as the context menu.

